blogData.title: We Are Participating in NSW Small Business Month 2022
blogData.description: NSW Small Business Month is running this November and VideoTranslatorAi is part of it!
blogData.keywords: nsw small business month, What month is nsw small business month?, What month is small business month?
blogData.coverAlt: Connect for success with NSW Small Business Month

data.richContent:
NSW Small Business Month is running this November and VideoTranslatorAi is a collaboration partner!

Join us and thousands of small businesses participating in the sixth NSW Small Business Month. There are hundreds of activities to choose from for small businesses in New South Wales. Learn about building your supply chain, leading your team, leveraging collaboration opportunities, diving into the latest social media trend for your small business, and many more!

Events are available online and face-to-face across New South Wales. It’s easy and free to take part in. Check out www.smallbusinessmonth.nsw.gov.au to find the event for you!

Let’s Connect for Success this #NSWSmallBizMonth.
